name: Rainbow Beetle Stretch
description: 000001•19•013432•697968  This generative piece was created by AI on the 17th May 2020, through careful selection of the piece’s parents (neither the subject of the final piece) and a guiding human hand, combining influence to create this unique and distinctive work. Reminiscent of a beetle as it stretches its unfeasably long appendages elegantly, catching the light to show the colour in its shell, which otherwise appears jet black.  Created by autre coeur. twitter / instagram @autrecoeur
